{
  "stem": "9730.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one thing I remember about-- actually, I was involved in two forts-- going with a German officer and walking first on the outside of the fort and seeing the cadavers of horses that had-- that had been killed in the shelling, you know, and all that, and this German officer bemoaning those poor animals, but having had absolutely no mercy, quite obviously.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he was more concerned about those horses than about human lives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when I went inside, I found there was a colonel in charge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after we exchanged the usual formalities and-- and I had time to talk to him, one of the first things he wanted to know from me-- this was now in probably November, November of '44-- he, of course, also bemoaned that it was necessary, you know, all this killing and so on.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he wanted to know, or he suggested that the logical thing would be for us to team up with them-- the Germans-- against the Russians.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I-- I asked him, you know, I-- I-- I asked him some questions about the-- you know, he-- he said something to me about, you know, why It was necessary for us to have taken this town or that town.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I said, well, you-- you didn't seem to mind taking these towns and-- and-- and-- and even, you know, bombing them-- Rotterdam and Coventry and all those places.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and-- and you didn't seem to mind-- because he tried to tell me, you know, how Germany didn't really want some of these things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, you didn't seem to mind your conquests.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he said, well, I have to admit one thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
